snippet.title: Saturn Longplay [076] Parodius
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Valis77

The Parodius series is a parody of the Gradius series of horizontal shooters.
This Sega Saturn release includes both the 1990 arcade version of 'Parodius' and it's 1994 arcade sequel 'Fantastic Journey' (AKA Gokujō Parodius!)

00:39 Parodius Playthrough
